            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 454,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "A curse is an effect that places some long-term affliction on a creature. Curses are always magical and are typically the result of a spell or trap. Effects with this trait can be removed only by effects that specifically target curses.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
